{
  "stem": "93.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But my next real encounter with them was after leaving Weimar, a few days later-- you know, I don't quite remember the exact days-- we liberated the city of Jena.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my contact with Jena was rather extensive because at this point, my colonel had, again, sent me on a mission to find a way through this city.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this city was now overrun by people that had escaped from the various concentration camps in the vicinity, as well as people trying to move east and get away.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I remember when I came to the city, my first sight, oddly enough, was a German man all dressed up in spats and I guess you'd call it a day coat.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was chopping stakes off a dead horse that was in the road, because everybody was starving, and there was no food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Everything had broken down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as I left him to go in, I reached the town square.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in the town square, there was a riot going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were hundreds-- hundreds of displaced people in here who were trying to break into the food stores that were in the square, where there was, of course, no food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And what they were doing was they were creating a tremendous block to the road which our regiment needed to get through in order to continue our movement to the east.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I remember at the time that I had a Tommy gun with me, which is a submachine gun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I fired across the head of the crowd.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that broke-- everybody scattered and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But as I continued on, I came to another crowd.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this was-- this was women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What it was was a storehouse that the Germans had set up for clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
